{"tid":1102920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青衣19歲少年被棍打搶錢 警拉7男女童黨","createTime":"2019-04-12T05:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-12T09:48:54.000Z","uid":3090,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"90d045378fe9a0de53965bf65c9900433fe883b6","tid":1102920,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Avy1DJu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvy1DJu.png&h=86de9716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵青警區反三合會調查組拘捕7名男女童黨。資料圖片(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n青衣長青邨青松樓對開公園，本月10日晚上8時許，一名19歲姓黃青年，被一批男女童用棍襲擊，背及腳受傷，同時被搶去2,500元。警員到場調查，並將事主送院治理。警方追緝涉案7名男童及3名女童。<br />\n<br />\n葵青警區反三合會調查組接手調查案件，昨日（11日）於葵青區內拘捕其中7人（4男3女），年齡介乎13至18歲，他們涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害及盜竊，現正被扣留調查。"},{"pid":"607c34d98d173bb9aebbace2e51ec23a4e81a668","tid":1102920,"uid":54502,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:33:07.000Z","msg":"多謝張超雄啦"},{"pid":"959d37a804d864db3dbc287db9dbc4831a3f1552","tid":1102920,"uid":90392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況如果被搶個位出手, 打死/打殘左啲仆街, <br />\n會唔會中刑事?<br />\n<br />\n純粹好奇問問。"},{"pid":"d7dc4bb076e77d6f6dd679b375b346a99070d0c3","tid":1102920,"uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"959d37a804d864db3dbc287db9dbc4831a3f1552","tid":1102920,"uid":90392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲情況如果被搶個位出手, 打死/打殘左啲仆街, <br />\n會唔會中刑事?<br />\n<br />\n純粹好奇問問。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"睇你係咪reasonable 咁用武力 打到人重傷 打死人咪unreasonable"},{"pid":"fce0518392ccdadf957f8243cee6e2bc3eaa9dc3","tid":1102920,"uid":90392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7dc4bb076e77d6f6dd679b375b346a99070d0c3","tid":1102920,"uid":75767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"959d37a804d864db3dbc287db9dbc4831a3f1552","tid":1102920,"uid":90392,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12